text: Je Jong-geel (; born March 21, 1955) is a South Korean politician. He was a member of the 17th National Assembly and the mayor of Ansan from 2014 to 2018. He is a member of the Chirwon Je clan. == References == Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:People from Changwon Category:Chirwon Je clan
title: Je Jong-geel
